  "faq": {
    "q1": "How does booking work?",
    "a1": "Search for your ideal property, select your dates and guests, then complete booking with secure payment via Stripe. You'll receive instant confirmation.",
    "q2": "What is your cancellation policy?",
    "a2": "Each property sets its own cancellation policy — Flexible, Moderate, Strict, or Non-refundable. Check the property listing for details before booking.",
    "q3": "How do I list my property?",
    "a3": "Sign up as an operator, complete the onboarding wizard, and add your property details including photos, pricing, and availability. It takes about 10 minutes.",
    "q4": "Are payments secure?",
    "a4": "All payments are processed through Stripe, a PCI-compliant payment processor. Your card details are never stored on our servers.",
    "q5": "Can I contact the host before booking?",
    "a5": "Yes! Each listing includes a message option to contact the host with any questions before you book.",
    "q6": "What if something goes wrong during my stay?",
    "a6": "Our support team is available to help resolve any issues. Contact us through the booking details page or email support@nfstay.app.",
    "q7": "How does the white-label feature work?",
    "a7": "Operators can create a branded booking website on their own subdomain (yourname.nfstay.app) or custom domain. Guests book directly with no nfstay branding visible.",
    "q8": "What is Hospitable integration?",
    "a8": "Hospitable integration allows property managers to sync their listings and calendars across multiple platforms, avoiding double bookings and manual updates."
  }
